---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<div class="relative w-full h-[420px] mb-24 overflow-hidden">

  <img
    src="/images/1111.jpg"
    alt="Company Building"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />

  <!-- overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>

  <!-- bottom banner -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 translate-y-1/2 z-10">

    <div class="bg-[#4a5d4e] py-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white text-4xl font-bold">About Us</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#e5edea] py-8 text-center shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-[#4a5d4e] text-3xl font-bold">
        XIAN YUHUI BIOTECHNOLOGY
      </h3>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- INTRO TEXT -->
<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
  <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-light">
    We combine in-house manufacturing in China with locally sourced raw materials and selected imported essential oils to provide a stable and flexible supply for global B2B customers.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- COMPANY SECTION -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <!-- TEXT -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4a5d4e]">The Company</h2>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        XIAN YUHUI BIOTECHNOLOGY is a trusted China-based manufacturer and supplier of essential oils, carrier oils, and customized oil blends. With over 11 years of industry experience, we combine in-house processing, reliable sourcing, and strict quality control to deliver consistent products for global B2B customers.
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We supply bulk essential oils to importers, wholesalers, cosmetic manufacturers, personal care brands, aromatherapy companies, and private label businesses worldwide. From sourcing and production to packaging and export support, our team provides flexible solutions tailored to different market requirements.
      </p>

     <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
       Whether you need single essential oils, carrier oils, or custom formulations, we are committed to helping your business grow through quality products, dependable supply, and professional service.
     </p>
    </div>

    <!-- IMAGE -->
    <div class="w-full">
      <img
        src="/images/banner-5.jpg"
        alt="Laboratory"
        class="w-full h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-xl object-cover"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-4 italic text-right">
        In-house quality control and manufacturing excellence
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- FLEXIBLE SUPPLY -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <!-- IMAGE -->
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/banner-4.jpg"
        alt="Business Partnership"
        class="w-full h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-xl object-cover"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-4 italic">
        Committed to collaborative growth and partnership
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- TEXT -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4a5d4e]">
        Flexible Supply for All Business Sizes
      </h2>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We provide flexible essential oil sourcing and manufacturing solutions tailored to different business needs. Whether you are an importer, distributor, cosmetic manufacturer, or private label brand, we can support customized specifications, packaging options, labeling requirements, and scalable order volumes.
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
       Our goal is to help customers build a stable and efficient supply chain through reliable quality, responsive service, and long-term partnership.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOURCE TO PRODUCT -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4a5d4e]">
        From Growers to Final Product
      </h2>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
       As an experienced essential oil manufacturer and supplier, we understand that product quality begins at the source. We carefully select botanical raw materials and work directly with trusted growers to ensure consistent quality, traceability, and sustainable supply
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our long-term sourcing partnerships enable us to provide stable bulk essential oil production and reliable supply solutions for customers around the world.
      </p>
    </div>

    <img
      src="/images/grower.jpg"
      class="w-full h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-xl object-cover"
      alt="Botanical Farming"
    />

  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUALITY CONTROL -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <img
      src="/images/lab-testing.jpg"
      class="w-full h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-xl object-cover"
      alt="Lab Testing"
    />

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4a5d4e]">
        Production & Quality Control System
      </h2>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our production is carried out in GMP-standard facilities supported by comprehensive quality control procedures. From raw material inspection and processing to filling and final packaging, each batch is monitored to ensure consistency, purity, and compliance with customer requirements.
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        In addition, our warehousing and inventory management systems help maintain product stability while providing full batch traceability throughout the supply chain.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section class="bg-[#e5edea] py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4a5d4e]">
        Contact our sales team
      </h2>

      <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Work with a professional essential oil manufacturer and explore tailored solutions for your business.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/images/contact-us.jpg"
        class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
        alt="Sales Team"
      />
    </div>

<form
  action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit"
  method="POST"
  class="space-y-4"
>

  <!-- Web3Forms Key -->
  <input
    type="hidden"
    name="access_key"
    value="5807e193-4a84-4b76-8713-b2b85da12526"
  />

  <!-- Subject -->
  <input
    type="hidden"
    name="subject"
    value="About Us Inquiry From Website"
  />

  <!-- Bot check -->
  <input
    type="checkbox"
    name="botcheck"
    class="hidden"
    style="display:none"
  />

  <input
    name="name"
    required
    class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg"
    placeholder="Your Name"
  />

  <input
    name="email"
    type="email"
    required
    class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg"
    placeholder="Your Email"
  />

  <input
    name="company"
    class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg"
    placeholder="Business"
  />

  <select
    name="country"
    class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg"
  >
    <option>United States - US</option>
    <option>United Kingdom - UK</option>
    <option>China</option>
    <option>Other</option>
  </select>

  <textarea
    name="message"
    required
    class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg"
    rows="4"
    placeholder="Message"
  ></textarea>

  <button
    type="submit"
    class="w-full bg-[#4a5d4e] text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90"
  >
    SUBMIT
  </button>

</form>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>